# Wallpapers are generated locally by wallpaper-generators/ and are intentionally
# NOT committed. This way update.sh can never restore a stale image over one you
# just regenerated. Run the generators (see wallpaper-generators/README.md) to
# (re)create them — they write into the folder below.
dotfiles/hypr/wallpapers/*.png

# Python caches
__pycache__/
*.pyc
